# DO commit:
#   terraform.tfvars         — placeholder values (must contain NO real IDs/tokens)
#   .terraform.lock.hcl      — Terraform dependency lockfile
#   uv.lock                  — uv (Python) dependency lockfile (one per component)
#   .python-version          — uv-managed Python version pin

